Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.91,2:05:50.09,JP_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あの子の命は ひこうき雲
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.19,2:03:24.74,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}白色坡道延绵至天际
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.72,2:03:34.91,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}蜉蝣飘舞于他的身旁
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.55,2:03:40.95,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不为人知 孑然一身
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.23,2:03:47.43,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他朝着远空飞翔
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.85,2:03:58.12,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}无所畏惧 飞舞升空
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.49,2:04:09.55,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}憧憬蓝天 奔向宇际
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.03,2:04:18.76,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他的生命就是那朵飞机云
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.76,2:04:32.15,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如今已无法得知
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.49,2:04:42.55,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他是否至死仍从窗户眺望那片蓝天
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.77,2:04:48.62,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他人无法理解
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.36,2:04:54.77,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只叹息他英年早逝
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.07,2:05:05.22,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}然而 他却是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.68,2:05:17.02,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}憧憬蓝天 奔向宇际
